{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"612","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"碳交易奏效 德國碳排年減7%","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/01/08 08:56</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%B8%9B%E7%A2%B3.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 534px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>再生能源<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年可滿足德國全國用電量的<span lang='EN-US'>42.6%</span>。圖為德國能源供應企業安能（<span lang='EN-US'>EnBW</span>）位於波羅的海的離岸風場<span lang='EN-US'>Baltic 2</span>。（<span lang='EN-US'>EnBW/J&ouml;rn Tirgrath</span>提供）中央社記者林育立柏林傳真<span lang='EN-US'> 108</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>日</span></span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社記者林育立柏林<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>日專電）歐洲實施碳交易制度，增加燃煤發電成本，成功發揮減碳的效果，德國的碳排量在去年減少了<span lang='EN-US'>7%</span>，朝減碳目標邁進。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>柏林能源轉型智庫<span lang='EN-US'>Agora Energiewende</span>今天公布年度報告，由於再生能源成長和碳交易制度的效應，德國<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年較前一年減少了<span lang='EN-US'>5000</span>萬噸、相當於<span lang='EN-US'>7%</span>的碳排量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>其中再生能源的部分，受風力條件良好和太陽能發電擴張的激勵，再生能源發電量首度超越燃煤火力發電和核電的總和，光風力、水力、太陽能和生質能等綠電即可滿足全國用電量的<span lang='EN-US'>42.6%</span>，比前一年成長<span lang='EN-US'>5%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>為控制碳排的總量，歐盟實施碳交易制度，業者購買碳權才能排放二氧化碳。由於碳權交易價格近年居高不下，許多燃煤火力發電廠為了避免虧損只好降載或停機，導致去年褐煤的發電量減少<span lang='EN-US'>22%</span>，煙煤的發電量減少<span lang='EN-US'>31%</span>，反之碳排量較少的天然氣發電量增加了<span lang='EN-US'>11%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>總計德國電力部門的碳排量在去年降低了<span lang='EN-US'>18%</span>，連續第<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>年下滑。全國碳排量與京都議定書基準年<span lang='EN-US'>1990</span>年相比降幅達<span lang='EN-US'>35%</span>，離<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>40%</span>的目標又更近一步。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>儘管電力部門減碳的成績高過預期，該智庫警告，建築和交通部門的碳排在去年不減反增，例如高碳排休旅車的熱賣，抵銷了電力部門減碳的成果。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>因此，該智庫建議，未來幾年，德國必須繼續擴充再生能源的裝置容量，才能彌補在<span lang='EN-US'>2022</span>年廢核後的電力缺口，並提供足夠的綠電給電動車和供應暖氣的熱汞使用，以減少交通和建築部門的碳排。（編輯：馮昭）<span lang='EN-US'>1090108</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202001080017.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-09","clk_count":"28"}},"__N_SSG":true}